us.fihgu.toolbox.reflection

Class WrapperBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • us.fihgu.toolbox.reflection.WrapperBase

  • public class WrapperBase
extends java.lang.Object
    This class wraps over another class though reflection
    You may invoke methods of the wrapped instance though invoke(String, Class, Class[], Object[]) method.

    Any child class of this class should have a @WrapsClass annotation.
